content.content: 燃烧弹药可以用在标准的自动加农炮和他们的近亲上.由来自恒星联邦的NAIS科学家开发,这些自动加农炮子弹包含一个炼狱弹头,并被一层薄薄的镁覆盖.

content.original: Precision AC Ammo carries self-guided gyrojet shells increasing accuracy. Upon receiving a Critical Hit, any remaining ammunition stored inside an Ammo Bin will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
content.prevOriginal: Precision AC Ammo carries self-guided gyrojet shells increasing accuracy. Upon receiving a Critical Hit, any remaining ammunition stored inside an Ammo Bin will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
content.content: 精密自动炮弹药携带着自制导陀螺稳定炮弹.在受到严重损伤后,储存在弹舱中的任何剩余弹药将爆炸,对安装部位造成伤害.使用C.A.S.E.可以降低风险.

content.original: C.A.S.E. ammunition bins are designed with blast plates facing away from vital components on a mech. Once sensors have detected an ammunition explosion the plate nearest to the outside is jettisoned. Resulting in much of the explosive potential to expand towards the free space outside and away from the mech.

Resulting in much of the explosive potential to expand towards the free space outside and away from the mech.
content.content: C.A.S.E.弹药箱的设计有爆炸面板以保护机甲上的重要部件.一旦传感器检测到弹药爆炸,靠近最外面的面板就被抛掉.将大量的爆炸能量导向机甲外部空间.
